  "prompt": "What is an example of a platform that leveraged another platform to gain users?",
  "response": "One prominent example of a platform leveraging another platform to gain users is Instagram's use of Facebook. When Instagram was initially launched, it allowed users to easily share their Instagram photos to Facebook, thereby gaining visibility among Facebook\u2019s vast user base. This integration helped Instagram quickly grow its user base by tapping into Facebook's established network. Additionally, after Facebook acquired Instagram in 2012, Instagram continued to benefit from Facebook's resources and infrastructure, further boosting its growth and popularity.",
